    <title>博客迁移到新电脑</title>
    <url>/hexo-migrate-to-new-computer/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h4 id="1-1-NodeJs"><a href="#1-1-NodeJs" class="headerlink" title="1.1 NodeJs"></a>1.1 <a href="https://nodejs.org/dist/v12.13.1/node-v12.13.1-x64.msi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NodeJs</a></h4><ul>
<li>1 <a href="https://nodejs.org/dist/v12.13.1/node-v12.13.1-x64.msi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">下载安装</a> </li>
<li>2 查看是否安装成功：添加到环境变量；node —version：输出版本号</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="1-2-hexo或hexo-cli"><a href="#1-2-hexo或hexo-cli" class="headerlink" title="1.2 hexo或hexo-cli"></a>1.2 hexo或hexo-cli</h4><ul>
<li><p><code>npm install -g hexo</code></p>
<ul>
<li><p>失败   nodejs版本要求 &gt;8</p>
</li>
<li><p>解析错误：<code>npm set registry https://registry.npmjs.org/</code>（更改镜像源）</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p><code>npm install -g hexo-cli</code>:有效</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="1-3-git"><a href="#1-3-git" class="headerlink" title="1.3 git"></a>1.3 git</h4><p>下载并安装git</p>
<h4 id="1-4-初始化"><a href="#1-4-初始化" class="headerlink" title="1.4 初始化"></a>1.4 初始化</h4><p>拷贝原先的文件</p>
<figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">_config.yml</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">package.json</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scaffolds/</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">source/</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">themes/</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>安装</p>
<figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">否则`hexo s`会失败</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---------------</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--------------</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> npm install hexo-generator-feed --save</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> npm install hexo-generator-sitemap --save</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
