<ul>
<li><p>1 <code>git config --global user.name &quot;mengki258&quot;</code></p>
</li>
<li><p>2 <code>git config --global user.email &quot;1710620635@qq.com&quot;</code></p>
</li>
<li><p>3 <code>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;1710620635@qq.com&quot;</code></p>
<ul>
<li><p>输入密码：password</p>
</li>
<li><p>保存位置</p>
<blockquote>
<p>认证信息： C:\Users{username}/.ssh/id_rsa.</p>
<p>公钥：C:\Users{username}/.ssh/id_rsa.pub.</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p>添加公钥到github的ssh上</p>
</li>
</ul>
